channel.title: Pwnscape dwarf_multi cannon/all nex sets with working effects/ summoning
channel.description:
pwnscape is a new 317 based rsps. we have many features that stand us appart from other servers. we have working dwarf multi cannon you can use for slayer or charm farming ecs. we have all nex sets with working hp boost. we have the max cape and the kiln cape. we have almost every current item all in a oldschool 317 server with 608 maps. if you are interested in playing our client can be downloaded here - http://uppit.com/fdpvgl2s06w5/pwnscape_client_v1.zip New client works for all java versions.
our webclient is under construction and should be up soon.
